query:
SELECT c.state, COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) as agencies, COUNT(p.id) as protocols
FROM counties c
LEFT JOIN protocolChunks p ON c.id = p.countyId
GROUP BY c.state
ORDER BY protocols DESC
LIMIT 25;
